Class GovernanceActionTypeUse

org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.relationships.GovernanceActionTypeUse.GovernanceActionTypeUse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class GovernanceActionTypeUse extends OMRSLine
GovernanceActionTypeUse is a relationships between an entity of type GovernanceActionType and an entity of type GovernanceAction. The ends of the relationships are stored as entity proxies, where there is a 'proxy' name by which the entity type is known. The first entity proxy has fromActionTypeTemplate as the proxy name for entity type GovernanceActionType. The second entity proxy has spawnedActions as the proxy name for entity type GovernanceAction. Each entity proxy also stores the entities guid. Link between a governance action type and a resulting governance action.
